snippet.title: Aliens Go Home Run! - Trailer 2
snippet.description:
We made a lot of changes since our first trailer and we are just about almost done. Look forward to playing all 70 levels soon! In the meantime, try out a free 5-level demo here: https://anim-ace.itch.io/aliens-go-home-run

Twitter: https://twitter.com/anim_ace
